---
const imgScreenshot = "/288fbc86b09c689d6a8b0f9d2c3e1919a64f610e.png";
const imgQuoteIcon = "/6d84d9a389dc1ca1fd84a84d019b93cf3a234d39.svg";
const imgDots = "/d2dbb4e9973def99004d59d871069a23974ee04c.svg";
---
<!-- background: radial-gradient(66.83% 66.83% at 50% 0%, #FFF 0%, #FFF6F4 100%); -->
<section style="background: radial-gradient(66.83% 66.83% at 50% 0%, #FFF 0%, #FFF6F4 100%)" class="flex flex-col gap-16 items-center px-[135px] py-32 w-full relative ">
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-center text-center w-full max-w-[1200px]">
		<h2 class="font-family-mona font-bold text-[52px] leading-[62px]">
			<span class="text-[#242c39]">Trusted by groomers</span>
			<span class="text-[#ff997e]"> around the world</span>
		</h2>
		<div class="font-family-mona font-normal text-[16px] leading-[30px] text-[#656689]">
			<p class="mb-0">
				Savvy Pet is trusted by over 1,500 pet professionals across the UK, US, Australia, New Zealand, Europe, and Canada — 
				<span class="font-bold">and growing fast.</span>
			</p>
			<p>Built to scale, easy to use, and loved worldwide.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="flex flex-col gap-12 items-center w-full max-w-[1170px]">
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 items-center w-full">
			<div class="flex flex-row gap-[30px] items-center w-full">
				<div 
					class="size-60 rounded-full border-4 border-[#ff997e] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat shrink-0"
					style={`background-image: url('${imgScreenshot}'); background-size: 114.48% 112%; background-position: 55.52% 48.33%;`}
				>
				</div>
				
				<div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#fff0ed] shadow-[0px_28px_46.1px_-28px_rgba(255,153,126,0.2)]">
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-9 p-10">
						<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full">
							<div class="size-8">
								<img src={imgQuoteIcon} alt="Quote" class="w-full h-full" />
							</div>
							
							<div class="font-family-mona font-normal text-[16px] leading-[30px] text-[#656689] text-left">
								<p class="mb-4">
									1 year after I opened my business, I knew I needed better booking software. I was using a well known software but the upgraded platform I needed was out of my price range. After months of research I decided on Savvy Pet Spa. It had what I needed at a price point I could manage. I am so happy I chose Savvy Pet Spa! The software is very user friendly and the Customer Service has been the absolute best!
								</p>
								<p class="mb-0">
									I can't say enough about how wonderful this company and the software they provide are. I've used them for over 4 yrs and plan to use them until I retire. Thank you Savvy Pet Spa!
								</p>
							</div>
							
							<div class="font-family-mona font-semibold text-[16px] leading-[30px] text-[#ff997e] text-left">
								— Gena Thompson CCE - The Captivating Canine Spa LLC, Ohio, USA
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="w-[114px] h-2.5">
			<img src={imgDots} alt="Pagination dots" class="w-full h-full" />
		</div>
	</div>
</section>